#: ../../certificates.rst:7
msgid ""
"An SSL/TLS certificate is a digital object issued by a Certificate Authority "
"(CA). The certificate is used to verify the identity of a host and to "
"establish encrypted communication channels. Upon installation, NethServer 8 "
"uses a default self-signed certificate for all TLS services, including the "
"Web user interface."
